WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'TriCon' is a Workbench game played on a triangular shaped
board, the idea is to rotate the links shown between the tiles
so they create a triangle on the outermost tiles of the board.
Complete the game in the least amount of moves possible.

  Have fun!

FEATURES
--------

-Simple installation: just run the game and play!

-Small package, the Lha archive is smaller than 50K, so it
 doesn't take ages to download :)

-The game plays on the Workbench screen and its window is
 resizeable.

